&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced with 5+ years of Product Marketing experience, specifically within Enterprise B2B SaaS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior full-funnel go-to-market experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience scaling a product in a multi-product B2B environment preferred&lt;/li&gt;
