&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to develop content, collateral, product positioning and messaging, as well as enablement assets&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about SaaS, cloud computing, FinOps and product-led growth strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
